s and expenses fund only does not include coinvestment the percentage of return is calculated as ending remaining investment fair market value plus net investment outflow sales proceeds minus net purchases minus beginning remaining investment fair market value divided by beginning remaining investment fair market value as of  investment funds and vehicles advised by alpinvest partners bv and metropolitan real estate equity management llc which comprise our investment solutions segment are included in our carry funds definition accordingly they are included in our invested capital realized proceeds and fund appreciation metrics for detailed definitions of the operating metrics above please see the carlyle group lps filings with the us securities and exchange commission about carlyle corporate overview purposemissionvalues the carlyle edge global investment resources history team operating executives  advisors geographic reach portfolio employees map industry awards careers corporate videos carlyle faqs our business business overview portfolio of investments industry expertise geographic reach value creation case studies illuminate most recent research commentary testimonies videos podcasts citizenship overview corporate citizenship reports media room overview news release archive value creation case studies annual reviews alerts and subscriptions corporate videos contact us creating value value creation case studies industry expertise global offices investor relations earning releases sec documents press releases events  presentations key metrics analyst coverage tax information distribution history unit information corporate governance investor faqs contact us contact us media worldwide offices investor relations careers   carlyle investment management llc all rights reserved home legalprivacy transparency  reporting microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies 