rting process all dashboards reports and charts can be accessed from any device and are completely integrated with microsoft excel the preqin solutions platform is designed to manage portfolios across different asset classes and investment strategies traditional buyouts venture capital infrastructure real estate debt and fund of funds third party integration with its state of the art api the preqin platform can integrate with any general ledger or crm system allowing consistent information across your back and front office systems avoiding manual reentry of data     preqin solutions powered by preqin solutions this website uses cookies to improve your experience well assume youre ok with this but you can optout if you wishok got it read more about us  peqin solutions formerly baxon solutions go to top call us      preqin solutions about us preqin solutions formerly baxon solutions is the leading innovator of cloud solutions to the private equity industry we believe that the private equity industry deserves better software to help it manage data and our firm aims to deliver simple functionality to enhance the quality of data and decision making tools available to portfolio companies through to the asset owners central to this objective is the belief that these tools should be accessible to all market participants and we aim to accommodate all firm sizes through a scalable pricing model and a lightweight solution that doesn’t require significant client resource to manage established in  we have built an extensive inhouse team of experienced consultants and financial analysts and accumulated a wealth of client and implementation best practices from our global customer base we provide a consultative approach to fully assess your business challenges to configure our solution to your needs preqin solutions is a subsidiary of preqin limited the leading source of information for the alternative assets industry providing data and analysis via online databases publications and bespoke data requests preqin’s products and services are utilized by more than  professionals located in over  countries for a range of activities including investor relations fundraising and marketing and market research founded in  the company operates from offices in london singapore new york austin san francisco buenos aires hong kong and manila why preqin solutions we are wholly focused on supporting and enhancing the portfolio management process allowing integration with legacy and best of breed bob systems our solution offers consistency and complete transparency in line with private equity directives such as aifmd and form pf and private equity industry alliances such as altexchange and investeurope our cloud solution offers significant time savings through automating manual processes and has proven to reduce the entire reporting process by over  no new hardware software or it support is required and the implementation period is  weeks by far the fastest in the industry most users require less than an hour of training we believe that the future relies on an agnostic web interface it is not a filebased system relying on an excel addin for those who choose to it can also interface with excel however finally through the integration of preqin data we have the unique ability to contextualize your fund performance relative to public and private markets more than just the data comes the insight through having access to the expectations of over  market participants given preqin’s global presence the companyabout us business cases partners careers contact how it works latest news beating the odds overcoming the challenges of firsttime fundraising preqin solutions enhances its commitment to securing your data announcing soc  type i carlos diaz our new vp of engineering private equity fundraising operational excellence in the midmarket the evolution of the private equity cfo   preqin solutions powered by preqin solutions this website uses cookies to improve your expe